Type: Package
Package: easysurv
Title: Estimate and Inspect Parametric Survival Models
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Niall", "Davison", , "niall.davison@maplehealthgroup.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Brad", "Kievit", , "brad.kievit@maplehealthgroup.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Functions to streamline the process of fitting parametric
    models to extrapolate survival data.  easysurv can fit data via
    simple parametric modelling, mixture cure modelling and spline
    modelling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Maple-Health-Group/easysurv,
